captions.text:
Hey Andrew, Andrew!
- Just keep it on the low.
- That is a cute hat, Quinta!
- Are you having a bad hair day?
Uh, did you need something else, or...
Hey look at me, I'm Quinta.
- Hey, you look really good in that hat.

- Yeah man, I think I might
have to stay late tonight.

It's not a big deal
but I just want to be--
- Did you get it on sale?

I just thought the only
thing better than a cute hat
is a cute hat half off!

But it looks like you
paid full price for it.

- [Voiceover] I wish
I had a hat like that.

title: Things That Happen When You Wear New Clothes
